title: Issue running Optical Character Recognition Demo
body:
I am trying to run OCR demo in my NUC
DISTRIB_ID=Ubuntu
DISTRIB_RELEASE=20.04
DISTRIB_CODENAME=focal
DISTRIB_DESCRIPTION="Ubuntu 20.04.4 LTS"
When i am tying to run the demo, i am getting the following issue:

**2022-09-19 04:25:22.702490: I tensorflow/core/platform/cpu_feature_guard.cc:193] This TensorFlow binary is optimized with oneAPI Deep Neural Network Library (oneDNN) to use the following CPU instructions in performance-critical operations:  AVX2 AVX512F AVX512_VNNI FMA

Please help with this.
